<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="eyebrow">admin</view>
    <view class="title">管理后台</view>
    <view class="summary">管理后端密钥、接口诊断、使用统计、失败次数和广告配置状态。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">使用统计</view>
    <view class="hint">统计来自 Worker KV，包含公开用户入口的生成、完成、失败、限流和无效密钥次数。</view>
    <button
      class="secondary"
      loading="{{loadingStats}}"
      disabled="{{loadingStats || !proxyAccessKey}}"
      bindtap="refreshAdminStats"
    >
      刷新统计
    </button>
    <view wx:if="{{statsResult}}" class="notice {{statsResultType}}">{{statsResult}}</view>

    <view class="stats-grid">
      <view class="stat-card" wx:for="{{statsCards}}" wx:key="label">
        <view class="stat-label">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="stat-value">{{item.value}}</view>
        <view class="stat-subtext">{{item.subtext}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="meta-list">
      <view class="meta-row" wx:for="{{statsMetaRows}}" wx:key="label">
        <view class="meta-label">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="meta-value">{{item.value}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">管理后台密钥</view>
    <view class="field">
      <view class="label">访问管理接口的口令</view>
      <input
        class="key-input"
        password
        value="{{proxyAccessKey}}"
        placeholder="粘贴管理后台密钥"
        bindinput="handleProxyKeyInput"
      />
    </view>
    <view class="hint">密钥只保存在当前微信本机存储里；普通用户生成解读不需要填写这个密钥。</view>

    <button class="primary" disabled="{{!proxyAccessKey}}" bindtap="saveProxyKey">保存到本机微信</button>
    <button wx:if="{{proxyKeySaved}}" class="secondary" bindtap="clearProxyKey">清除本机密钥</button>
    <button
      class="secondary"
      loading="{{testingBackend}}"
      disabled="{{testingBackend || !proxyAccessKey}}"
      bindtap="testBackend"
    >
      测试后端连接
    </button>
    <view class="hint">测试会发送一次最小提示词到 Worker 和模型服务，用于确认合法域名、访问密钥和后端链路是否正常。</view>

    <view wx:if="{{notice}}" class="notice {{noticeType}}">{{notice}}</view>
    <view wx:if="{{backendTestResult}}" class="notice {{backendTestType}}">{{backendTestResult}}</view>
    <button class="secondary compact-action" bindtap="copyDiagnostics">复制诊断信息</button>
    <view class="hint">诊断信息不包含密钥，只包含域名、接口、密钥保存状态和后端测试结果。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">微信平台域名</view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">request 合法域名</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{requestDomain}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{requestDomain}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">web-view 业务域名</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{webviewDomain}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{webviewDomain}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">LLM 请求接口</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{apiUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{apiUrl}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">LLM 后台任务接口</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{llmJobUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{llmJobUrl}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">公开用户任务接口</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{publicLlmJobUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{publicLlmJobUrl}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>

    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">管理统计接口</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{adminStatsUrl}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{adminStatsUrl}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">广告配置</view>
    <view class="hint">{{adStatusText}}</view>
    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">原生模板广告 unit-id</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{adCustomUnitId || '未配置'}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{adCustomUnitId}}" disabled="{{!adCustomUnitId}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>
    <view class="domain-row">
      <view class="domain-main">
        <view class="domain-title">Banner 广告 unit-id</view>
        <view class="domain-value">{{adBannerUnitId || '未配置'}}</view>
      </view>
      <button class="copy-button" data-value="{{adBannerUnitId}}" disabled="{{!adBannerUnitId}}" bindtap="copyValue">复制</button>
    </view>
    <view class="hint">广告单元 ID 需要在微信小程序后台的流量主模块创建；无广告返回时前台会自动隐藏广告区域。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">本机数据管理</view>
    <view class="hint">清除当前微信本机保存的访问密钥、出生信息、发送确认、后台任务和解读历史；不会影响 Cloudflare、微信后台或服务器配置。</view>
    <button class="danger-button" bindtap="clearLocalData">清除本机数据</button>
  </view>

  <view class="panel">
    <view class="panel-title">下一步测试</view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="openNativeApp">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">回到原生排盘</view>
        <view class="row-text">用已保存密钥并勾选发送确认，生成一次 LLM 解读</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
    <view class="row" bindtap="openCompliance">
      <view>
        <view class="row-title">合规说明</view>
        <view class="row-text">查看隐私、娱乐参考与使用边界文案</view>
      </view>
      <view class="chevron">›</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
